{"tid":2078830,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"富臨再發盈警　大幅調升虧損至 6.5 億","createTime":"2020-06-25T10:34:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T11:19:43.000Z","uid":39464,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"6636fc3b4c62e55727a2426effe6c1aa4ce86e1b","tid":2078830,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T10:34:44.000Z","msg":"富臨（1443）發出盈利警告，料去年業績盈轉虧；截至今年 3 月底止年度將錄得約 6 億至 6.5 億元虧損，去年同期賺 2,550 萬元。<br />\n<br />\n富臨於今年 5 月已發過一次盈利警告，當時預期去年度業績虧損超過 2 億元，時隔個多月，集團指掌握到的額外資料，相信虧損狀況遠多於 5 月時的預測，主要原因包括：整體收益比上年度減少介乎兩成六至三成二；涉及廠房、商譽等減值虧損 2.5 億元；錄得投資物業、金融資產等公平值虧損。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/finance/%E5%AF%8C%E8%87%A8%E5%86%8D%E7%99%BC%E7%9B%88%E8%AD%A6-%E5%A4%A7%E5%B9%85%E8%AA%BF%E5%8D%87%E8%99%A7%E6%90%8D%E8%87%B3-6-5-%E5%84%84/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%25E5%25AF%258C%25E8%2587%25A8%25E5%2586%258D%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%259B%2588%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B9%2585%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E5%258D%2587%25E8%2599%25A7%25E6%2590%258D%25E8%2587%25B3-6-5-%25E5%2584%2584%2F&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfeBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=58c532c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%25E5%25AF%258C%25E8%2587%25A8%25E5%2586%258D%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%259B%2588%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B9%2585%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E5%258D%2587%25E8%2599%25A7%25E6%2590%258D%25E8%2587%25B3-6-5-%25E5%2584%2584%2F&h=b504d0d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/finance/%E5%AF%8C%E8%87%A8%E5%86%8D%E7%99%BC%E7%9B%88%E8%AD%A6-%E5%A4%A7%E5%B9%85%E8%AA%BF%E5%8D%87%E8%99%A7%E6%90%8D%E8%87%B3-6-5-%E5%84%84/</a>"},{"pid":"07dd7f61ce86cae29bcc38157a8b21719727743c","tid":2078830,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T10:36:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mbxE55hyYzQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dm